		<title>Lt. Gov. Polito Addressed Graduates During Commencement</title>
		<link>https://www.becker.edu/lt-gov-polito-addressed-graduates-during-commencement/</link>
		<comments>https://www.becker.edu/lt-gov-polito-addressed-graduates-during-commencement/#respond</comments>
